OL,3,C'Unforgivable': Report finds death of
OL,4,Clearning disabled man was preventable
OL,6,FPaul Scriven says his nephew Myles'
OL,7,Fdeath must be a watershed moment in
OL,8,Fhow people with learning disabilities
OL,9,Fare treated in the health service, as
OL,10,FITV News Investigations Editor Daniel
OL,11,FHewitt reports
OL,13,FA coroner has issued a damning report
OL,14,Fagainst an NHS hospital trust
OL,15,Ffollowing the entirely preventable
OL,16,Fdeath of a 31-year-old autistic man
OL,17,Fwith learning disabilities, branding
OL,18,Fthe attitude of doctors "dismissive
OL,19,Fand complacent".
