OL,3,C'Unforgivable': Report finds death of
OL,4,Clearning disabled man was preventable
OL,6,FMyles became unwell in late 2022 with
OL,7,Fshortness of breath and a blood clot
OL,8,Fin his leg. He was prescribed
OL,9,FRivaroxaban - a blood thinning
OL,10,Fmedication - but despite taking the
OL,11,Fpill every day as prescribed, months
OL,12,Flater he was still unwell.
OL,14,FA consultant haematologist recommended
OL,15,Fswitching Myles' medication to a
OL,16,Fdifferent blood thinner - Warfarin -
OL,17,Fbut Myles' doctor instead assumed
OL,18,FMyles was not taking the drug and
OL,19,Fopted to keep Myles on Rivaroxaban.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/17
