OL,3,C'Unforgivable': Report finds death of
OL,4,Clearning disabled man was preventable
OL,6,FWhen in March 2023, Myles was again
OL,7,Fsuffering with shortness of breath,
OL,8,Fhis GP surgery offered him a telephone
OL,9,Fconsultation, despite Myles' stated
OL,10,Fissues with communication.
OL,12,FMyles was struggling to breathe
OL,13,Fnormally but he was not referred to
OL,14,FA&E. He was seen again by the GP three
OL,15,Fdays later but was again not sent to
OL,16,Fhospital.
OL,18,FThree weeks later, Myles collapsed and
OL,19,Fwas rushed Huddersfield Royal
OL,20,FInfirmary, where he later died from a
OL,21,Fpulmonary embolism.
