OL,3,C'Unforgivable': Report finds death of
OL,4,Clearning disabled man was preventable
OL,6,FDespite his family flagging with
OL,7,Fhealthcare professionals that he had a
OL,8,Flearning disability and was autistic,
OL,9,Fand would require help to make medical
OL,10,For treatment decisions, his two uncles
OL,11,F- who were his stated medical
OL,12,Fadvocates - were never contacted by
OL,13,Fthe hospital or GP either in late 2022
OL,14,For spring 2023.
OL,16,F"For all intents and purposes, other
OL,17,Fthan his learning disability and
OL,18,Fautism, Myles was physically well,"
OL,19,Fsaid David Black, Paul's husband and
OL,20,FMyles' uncle.
