OL,6,F"Hearing that this was preventable -
OL,7,Fthat Myles could have been saved on at
OL,8,Fleast three occasions - was really,
OL,9,Freally difficult," he said.
OL,11,F"If we had been called, we would have
OL,12,Fbeen able to support Myles in making a
OL,13,Fdecision that would have probably
OL,14,Fsaved his life."
