OL,3,C'Unforgivable': Report finds death of
OL,4,Clearning disabled man was preventable
OL,6,FOfficial data shows that men with a
OL,7,Flearning disability die 20 years
OL,8,Fearlier than the general population in
OL,9,Fthe UK. Women with a learning
OL,10,Fdisability die on average 23 years
OL,11,Fyounger.
OL,13,FProfessor Sara Ryan researches social
OL,14,Fcare with a specialism in learning
OL,15,Fdisabilities and autism. Her own son,
OL,16,FConnor Sparrowhawk, who was learning
OL,17,Fdisabled, autistic and had epilepsy,
OL,18,Fdied in 2013 whilst in the care of an
OL,19,FNHS assessment facility.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/17
