OL,3,C'Unforgivable': Report finds death of
OL,4,Clearning disabled man was preventable
OL,6,F"I was struck by how similar Myles'
OL,7,Fdeath was to Connor's in that he died
OL,8,Fthrough the most woeful failings of
OL,9,Fhealthcare," she told ITV News.
OL,11,F"Connor was left to drown in a bath in
OL,12,Fa hospital unit, and he had diagnosed
OL,13,Fepilepsy."
OL,15,F"We have to remember that people with
OL,16,Flearning disabilities aren't ill,"
OL,17,FProfessor Ryan said.
