OL,3,C'Unforgivable': Report finds death of
OL,4,Clearning disabled man was preventable
OL,6,F"There's no reason why people should
OL,7,Fbe dying so early. You have got a
OL,8,Ftsunami of evidence that says we know
OL,9,Fwhy people are dying, we know how
OL,10,Fpeople are dying, and we are doing
OL,11,Fnothing about it."
OL,13,FOutside Bradford Coroner's Court,
OL,14,FMyles' uncles reflected on the
OL,15,Fjudgement.
OL,17,F"It was very raw listening to the full
OL,18,Flist of times Myles could have been
OL,19,Fsaved."
