OL,3,C'Unforgivable': Report finds death of
OL,4,Clearning disabled man was preventable
OL,6,FBrendan Brown, Chief Executive of
OL,7,FCalderdale and Huddersfield NHS
OL,8,FFoundation Trust, said: "My sincere
OL,9,Fcondolences go out to Myles' family
OL,10,Fand his loved ones. We have formally
OL,11,Fapologised to Myles' family, but we
OL,12,Ffully acknowledge that no apology can
OL,13,Fcompensate for the profound impact of
OL,14,Fwhat has occurred, nor for the
OL,15,Ffailings identified within the Trust.
