OL,3,C'Unforgivable': Report finds death of
OL,4,Clearning disabled man was preventable
OL,6,F"We accept the coroner's findings in
OL,7,Ffull. We will ensure these are used to
OL,8,Fbuild upon the changes made as a
OL,9,Fresult of the Trust's internal review
OL,10,Fand the clinical lessons learned from
OL,11,FMyles' sad death.
OL,13,F"We acknowledge the concerns that
OL,14,Fthere is more which we could have done
OL,15,Fto involve Myles' family in his care
OL,16,Fand are acting on this as a Trust."
